<p><strong>Hotel phrases:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>WiFi密码是什么？(WiFi mìmǎ shì shénme?) — What's the WiFi password?</li>
  <li>可以换一个房间吗？(Kěyǐ huàn yī gè fángjiān ma?) — Can I change rooms?</li>
  <li>空调不工作了。(Kōngtiáo bù gōngzuò le.) — The AC isn't working.</li>
  <li>热水不热。(Rè shuǐ bú rè.) — The hot water isn't hot.</li>
  <li>可以寄存行李吗？(Kěyǐ jìcún xínglǐ ma?) — Can I store my luggage?</li>
